{"tid":1191617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 假色情App誘民眾付費觀看　警拘33詐騙疑犯","createTime":"2019-06-08T04:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T04:20:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0f041681859d169d65c34640f31afb03cb76c29f","tid":1191617,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"廣東揭陽市警方近日搗破一個詐騙集團，疑犯利用假流動應用程式（App），誘騙受害人付費觀看假色情影片，以圖無本生利。行動中警方拘捕並刑事拘留33名疑犯，凍結涉案資金500多萬元人民幣（逾580萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n今年3月25日警方接獲民眾報案，稱其在一款色情App上按照要求多次充值後，仍無法觀看程式內的影片，懷疑遭人詐騙。隨後陸續有受害人報案，警方懷疑該App存在詐騙行為，且涉案數額巨大。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查發現，該詐騙集團不僅有組織、有規模，且成員遍布深圳、清遠，以及湖南、江蘇、廣西等地。及至上月16日，警方兵分多路展開收網行動拘捕疑犯，並在涉案窩點合共繳獲48部電腦、58部手機、凍結帳號869個。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190606/bkn-20190606094250308-0606_00952_001.html?view=d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190606%2Fbkn-20190606094250308-0606_00952_001.html%3Fview%3Dd&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW85hvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=78c43a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190606/bkn-20190606094250308-0606_00952_001.html?view=d</a>"},{"pid":"e4a72d311b2fb683f2dcb1ad3af93198039ff1d9","tid":1191617,"uid":90392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為係仙..."},{"pid":"ef788eef22268dd47c825e158ff557f76940e8ed","tid":1191617,"uid":5993,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4a72d311b2fb683f2dcb1ad3af93198039ff1d9","tid":1191617,"uid":90392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為係仙..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"我都以為係"},{"pid":"3b700bc886674b0c5571aa519dc3d8681e22177b","tid":1191617,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:54:15.000Z","msg":"Don&rsquo;t pay any attention to such apps. They&rsquo;re scammers who sell us a bill of goods for a living."},{"pid":"3aba6ca